author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
We're back with The Indie Hour Episode Twenty-One! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

Ready to leave dice behind? Use your MATH skills to stack stat block bonuses for this hyper-detailed skirmish, role-play and mass-combat Battler set in a realm abandoned by the Fae. Play as a variety of mythical creatures on the outskirts of a fallen land once held together by magic and mystecism. It's THE WOODS!

Check out the WOODS Rulebook HERE: https://www.wargamevault.com/product/275714/The-Woods-Second-Edition-Dark-Age-Folklore-Fantasy-Core-Rulebook-rules-for-Skirmish-RPG-and-Masscombat?affiliate_id=210041
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 021 - THE WOODS 2nd Edition
